casebody.data:
Jeanne FINNEGAN, Plaintiff,
v.
INDUCTOTHERM CORP., Defendant/Third-Party Plaintiff-Respondent,
v.
Greentree Food Management, Inc., Third-Party Defendant/Fourth-Party Plaintiff-Petitioner,
v.
Fred Dunhour and The Dunhour Agency, Fourth-Party Defendants-Petitioners. C-366 September Term 2017
080086 Supreme Court of New Jersey. November 29, 2017

To the Appellate Division, Superior Court:

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-004267-15 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied, with costs.
